OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOvernight low cloud gradually
OL,6,Fburning back to eastern coastal
OL,7,Fdistricts through the morning, then
OL,8,Flingering in places into the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Otherwise it will be dry
OL,10,Fand sunny. Very warm, locally hot in
OL,11,Fin the west. Cooler in the east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,14,Flate sunshine. Then the rest of the
OL,15,Fnight will be dry, but some low cloud
OL,16,Fdeveloping across the east. Clear in
OL,17,Fthe west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
