OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FDry with hazy sunshine, but
OL,6,Flow cloud may linger along North Sea
OL,7,Fcoasts and coastal parts of the
OL,8,Fnorthwest. Very warm or hot inland.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FCloudy
OL,11,Fstart Friday otherwise dry and bright,
OL,12,Ffar north remaining cloudy. Cloudier
OL,13,Fon Saturday, chance of a light shower
OL,14,Fat first in the north. Mainly dry and
OL,15,Fbright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
